{"tid":2044613,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國證實正尋找新5G建造商取代華為","createTime":"2020-05-31T08:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T04:55:18.000Z","uid":28765,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9d630685fc566dc39cd7d7ce2adca3dfffbdb708","tid":2044613,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:21:57.000Z","msg":"即時新聞／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n從中國向全球蔓延的武漢肺炎疫情（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19），引發全球反中浪潮，也連帶影響中國5G行動通訊技術的全球版圖。英國首相強森發言人日前證實，該國正尋找新5G網路建設參與者，以減少對中國設備大廠華為（Huawei）的依賴，。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》 報導，近來英國一直希望減少對華為在5G網路的依賴。強森的發言人James Slack 上週五（29日）證實，該國早在今年1月起，就開始尋找新的5G網路建設參與者，並同時也在研究因應美國對華為實施得新制裁，可能對該國造成的影響。<br />\n<br />\n此外，英國也在早前促請美國帶頭籌組10個民主國家聯盟（「D10聯盟」），希望透過包括資助D10聯盟內既有的電信企業等方法，建立5G網路設備和相關技術供應商的替代名單，打破中國壟斷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3182688\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3182688&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdNjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=8c0ef296\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3182688&h=ce3cf88e\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3182688</a>"},{"pid":"328c486f5629b52db92ec8bd326d2cfdbc9a55e8","tid":2044613,"uid":30768,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TvPLS4g.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTvPLS4g.gif&h=0323065c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5f97115a7d8f7326934fe46d705404e86e1d917","tid":2044613,"uid":292591,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9d630685fc566dc39cd7d7ce2adca3dfffbdb708","tid":2044613,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:21:57.000Z","msg":"即時新聞／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n從中國向全球蔓延的武漢肺炎疫情（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19），引發全球反中浪潮，也連帶影響中國5G行動通訊技術的全球版圖。英國首相強森發言人日前證實，該國正尋找新5G網路建設參與者，以減少對中國設備大廠華為（Huawei）的依賴，。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》 報導，近來英國一直希望減少對華為在5G網路的依賴。強森的發言人James Slack 上週五（29日）證實，該國早在今年1月起，就開始尋找新的5G網路建設參與者，並同時也在研究因應美國對華為實施得新制裁，可能對該國造成的影響。<br />\n<br />\n此外，英國也在早前促請美國帶頭籌組10個民主國家聯盟（「D10聯盟」），希望透過包括資助D10聯盟內既有的電信企業等方法，建立5G網路設備和相關技術供應商的替代名單，打破中國壟斷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3182688\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3182688&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdNjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=8c0ef296\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3182688&h=ce3cf88e\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3182688</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:26:37.000Z","msg":"做比人睇姐 英國人做野積唔積極大家心知"},{"pid":"b3482280803317d31a1455f74998b6a0173c5964","tid":2044613,"uid":19012,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:28:28.000Z","msg":"只要華為收購Ericsson及 Nokia 咁就無對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67dbce5faf2eeb74c65606d6b2846bf8d77514cb","tid":2044613,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:30:42.000Z","msg":"華為=大廠？"},{"pid":"a9c4c0ef8783a41eb139ee7604b93be0fe070d41","tid":2044613,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:31:48.000Z","msg":"一早叫佢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e5f307a2007791a1b854b9d68157156b87e825","tid":2044613,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67dbce5faf2eeb74c65606d6b2846bf8d77514cb","tid":2044613,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:30:42.000Z","msg":"華為=大廠？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:32:38.000Z","msg":"國家做後盾無限金錢"},{"pid":"e6f82f31aff40ff6db39880a2475ade12dea1156","tid":2044613,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci